{"tid":1528467,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"喂你地扑玻璃逃生可唔可以扑得專業啲呀","createTime":"2019-09-01T14:08:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T14:24:26.000Z","uid":96930,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"def1f4328990093bf7831b947f73047aab1b1a52","tid":1528467,"uid":96930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:08:30.000Z","msg":"扑玻璃要扑四角呀！扑四角先最易爛呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />扑中間仲要搵啲唔夠尖嘅野去扑會扑到下世架！中信個陣又係扑玻璃門嘅中間，咪扑唔穿囉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GGsqOK6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGGsqOK6.png&h=d005333e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拿咁樣做呢係犯法嘅 千其唔好做呀你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係萬一你地有日要緊急逃生扑玻璃窗呢，就記得要扑四角，唔好扑中間喇！<br />\n<br />\n「至於乘客若拿不到手錘，有專家建議只要隨手拿來尖的硬物也可擊爆玻璃，例如高跟鞋踭，但注意必須敲打4角及邊緣位置，才能擊破玻璃，否則胡亂敲打，可能徒勞無功。另有專家建議在危急時，乘客應各自用尖物，合力敲擊4角，就能以最短時間擊破玻璃逃生。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1469074/巴士遇火警點算？硬物敲碎玻璃窗四角急逃生\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1469074%2F%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E9%81%87%E7%81%AB%E8%AD%A6%E9%BB%9E%E7%AE%97%EF%BC%9F%E7%A1%AC%E7%89%A9%E6%95%B2%E7%A2%8E%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83%E7%AA%97%E5%9B%9B%E8%A7%92%E6%80%A5%E9%80%83%E7%94%9F&d=3Z9ZeYaQzwHPi2iIp4702CpZd1NrJsyKidS%2BVLva3MM%3D&h=61ceeca9\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1469074/巴士遇火警點算？硬物敲碎玻璃窗四角急逃生</a><br />\n<br />\n呢啲逃生嘅常識大家都要識呀屌！ 黨鐵一陣又有咩意外都可以幫到大家走呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b38f070439e6e9d2d6cdd30019e368b47cc781e","tid":1528467,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:14:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb3d9b10a84f78094872a9733dff08fa3fb9def4","tid":1528467,"uid":239250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:14:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c80277dab36562a258ab411f6e695622d0e2d8a5","tid":1528467,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:15:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n寧鳴而死 不默而生<br />\n寧化飛灰 不作浮塵</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"be86519f7ba90e012eddf314a1fc3dd963fcce54","tid":1528467,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:22:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fc6de48edcd00a3096263c5eb11dc917825ba43","tid":1528467,"uid":304180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:24:25.000Z","msg":"不完美，可改善。每天也在學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6dc699b490c532a14b3de418488d66da5dd5f0c","tid":1528467,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:24:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}